source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_SEQ_00<tab>789th Order Dustman Bo Zu is looking for an adventurer to defuse a problem of burgeoning proportions.
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_SEQ_00<tab>Im Abbaugebiet des 789. Ordens fürchtet sich Bo Zu vor Ba Go.

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_SEQ_01<tab>Angered by the attention Ba Go lavishes upon his younger, prettier creations, a trio of breeding bombs has broken free from the acolyte's workshop and are wreaking havoc around Iron Lake. Quell their rage with a good beating and return their cores to Bo Zu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_SEQ_01<tab>Bo Zu fürchtet, dass Ba Go die Beherrschung verlieren könnte, weil ihm seine <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20A80030202 /var> entwischt sind. Offensichtlich braucht er sie nicht in heilem Zustand zurück, sondern nur ihre Essenzen. Besiege die drei entflohenen <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20A80030502 /var> und stelle ihre Essenzen sicher.

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_SEQ_02<tab>You have defused the threat and acquired the three cores. Return to the 789th Order Dig and hand the fruits of your labor to Bo Zu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_SEQ_02<tab>Du hast <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8931030502 /var> sichergestellt. Bring sie zu Bo Zu im Abbaugebiet des 789. Ordens.

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_SEQ_03<tab>Bo Zu expresses his gratitude for your efforts. Though it was originally his intention to return the cores to Ba Go, the dustman has reconsidered, fearing that this would further fan the flames of jealousy harbored by the acolyte's volatile beauties...
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_SEQ_03<tab>Bo Zu ist sichtlich erleichtert, dass du ihm <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8931030502 /var> gebracht hast. Daraus kann Ba Go neue Bomber züchten, was ihn deutlich aufmuntern dürfte. Bo Zu hofft nur, dass die neuen Exemplare umgänglicher sind und nicht so exzentrisch wie ihr Züchter.

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_TODO_00<tab>Slay breeding bombs and obtain their cores.
TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_TODO_01<tab>Deliver bomb cores to 789th Order Dustman Bo Zu.
TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_000<tab>They're going to blow─burst, blast, blow! Who? Three of Ba Go's beauties, yes, yes, that is who!
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_000<tab>Ba Go kleines Problem hat. Seine <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20A80030202 /var> ihm entwischt sind!

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_001<tab>And not just any beauties─no, no, they are the mothers of all beauties. Ba Go's very first creations. Ba Go spends too much time with his newest creations, and their mothers are not happy─no, no, not happy at all.
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_001<tab>Gar nicht gut! Bestimmt stinksauer er ist. Und wenn er sauer, dann furchtbar explosiv! Seine Bomber fürchterlich sind, ganz gefährlich! Ihn schnell beruhigen, ja?

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_002<tab>They escape to Iron Lake, where they seethe with anger─fume, swell, seethe─and Ba Go is too smitten with his newfound lovelies to notice. You must cool their ire, yes, and bring their cores back to me. You bring them to me, and I bring them to Ba Go, that gentler beauties may be born.
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_002<tab>Ganz schnell zu Eisensee du gehst und Essenzen von <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20A80030402 /var> holst und zu mir bringst, ja? Ja, ja!

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_003<tab>Three of Ba Go's beauties have escaped to Iron Lake. Yes, they seethe with anger─fume, swell, seethe─and Ba Go is too smitten with his newfound lovelies to notice. You must cool their ire, yes, and bring their cores back to me, that gentler beauties may be born.
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_003<tab>Ganz schnell zu Eisensee du gehst und <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E8931030502 /var> von <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20A80030402 /var> holst und zu mir bringst, ja? Ja, ja!

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_100_020<tab>You return with the cores─yes, yes you do?
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_100_020<tab>Na, na? Geschafft du hast? Geflohene Bomber erwischt du hast? <var 2B ((<var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E8931030502 /var>)) /var> gebracht du hast, ja?

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_020<tab>You have my gratitude, adventurer─my thanks, my appreciation, my gratitude. The last time Ba Go's beauties escaped, they almost burned poor Bo Zu's nose off. Yes, yes, they did.
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_020<tab>Ja, ja! Genau richtig! Daraus Ba Go kann neue Bomber züchten. Dann er nicht mehr zornig! Danke, danke!

source: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_021<tab>Bo Zu thinks Ba Go has more beauties than he knows what to do with. Maybe these cores are better kept here─yes, kept safe and quiet in the hands of Bo Zu...
target: TEXT_BANKOB105_01329_BOZU_000_021<tab>Hoffentlich neue Bomber werden ruhiger. Oft sie sind ganz merkwürdig, wie ihr Vater.
